<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Accept Ownership Transfer</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f8fbff;
      color: #111827;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }
    .wrapper {
      width: 100%;
      table-layout: fixed;
      background-color: #f8fbff;
      padding: 40px 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 540px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border: 1.5px solid rgba(0, 153, 255, 0.08);
      border-radius: 18px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 153, 255, 0.06);
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7c3aed 0%, #a855f7 100%);
      padding: 30px 40px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 40px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .content h2 {
      margin-top: 0;
      color: #7c3aed;
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.3px;
    }
    .content p {
      color: #4b5563;
      font-size: 15px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .action-box {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    .btn-accept {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 14px 30px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7c3aed 0%, #a855f7 100%);
      color: #ffffff !important;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 15px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.35);
      transition: all 0.2s ease;
    }
    .footer {
      padding: 0 40px 40px 40px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .footer p {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #9ca3af;
      margin: 0 0 8px 0;
    }
    .warning {
      color: #b91c1c !important;
      font-weight: 600;
      background: #fef2f2;
      border: 1px solid #fee2e2;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 12px;
      font-size: 13.5px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>RelayFlow</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <h2>Ownership Transfer Request</h2>
        <p>Hello <strong><%= displayName %></strong>,</p>
        <p>An ownership transfer request has been initiated for you to become the new owner of the group/server: <strong><%= groupName %></strong>.</p>
        
        <p class="warning">
          ⚠️ <strong>Important Security Warning:</strong> Accepting this transfer will make you the primary owner of the group. You will assume full responsibility, including permissions management and server controls.
        </p>

        <div class="action-box">
          <a href="<%= acceptLink %>" class="btn-accept">Accept Ownership Transfer</a>
        </div>
        
        <p>This request link will expire in 24 hours. If you did not request or expect this transfer, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> RelayFlow. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>Vibrant & Secure Real-Time Messaging Platform.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
